<paragraph blockId="14.[313,1269,180,560]" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">
<emphasis box="[353,494,375,399]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">Distribution.</emphasis>
This species occurs from the Brazilian state of Espírito Santo State (latitude 
<geoCoordinate box="[417,469,407,431]" degrees="20" direction="south" orientation="latitude" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438" precision="55555" value="-20.0">20°S</geoCoordinate>
), to RS, and there is a doubtful record of it in 
<collectingRegion box="[991,1144,407,431]" country="Argentina" name="Ciudad Autonoma de Buenos Aires" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">Buenos Aires</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1154,1268,407,431]" name="Argentina" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">Argentina</collectingCountry>
(Lemos de Castro, 1958; Araujo 
<emphasis box="[715,769,439,463]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">et al</emphasis>
., 1996). This species has previously been recorded in RS in the regions of Fontoura Xavier and Erexim (Araujo 
<emphasis box="[1132,1181,472,496]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="2438">et al</emphasis>
., 1996) and this record increases the known range of the species to the north-east region of RS.
</paragraph>
